(1, 'Apple iPad Pro M4', 'The ultimate iPad experience in an ultra-thin design. Features the breakthrough tandem OLED Liquid Retina XDR display, outrageous performance of the Apple M4 chip, and superfast wireless connectivity.', 999.00, 25, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544244015-0df4b3ffc6b0?w=600&q=80', 'Smart Devices', 4.9),
